Method Detail

initializeParsers

protected void initializeParsers()
Description copied from class: OWSParserContext
Loads the parser map with the parser to use for each element type. The parser may be changed by calling BasicXMLEventParserContext.registerParser(javax.xml.namespace.QName, gov.nasa.worldwind.util.xml.XMLEventParser).

Overrides:
initializeParsers in class WFSParserContext

initializeWFSParsers

protected void initializeWFSParsers(String ns)
Loads parsers for the WFS schema.

Compatible with WFS version 2.0.0.

See http://schemas.opengis.net/wfs/2.0/wfs.xsd.

Overrides the default WFS FeatureType parser with the WSS FeatureType parser.

Overrides:
initializeWFSParsers in class WFSParserContext
Parameters:
ns - ns the XML namespace used to construct the element parsers. This namespace is passed as the sole parameter to each XML element parser's constructor.
